data.description: Stunning custom beach house designed by architect Al Hansen, restored to perfection. Features chef's kitchen with original fir floors, farmhouse style sink, and limestone countertops. Relax with loved ones in the spacious living & dining room with stone gas fireplace, exposed beams, and vaulted ceilings. 2 ensuite bedrooms downstairs, plus primary suite with balcony & view of the Pacific Ocean, spa-inspired bathroom,  and office space. The charm continues through the French doors to the beautifully manicured outdoor areas with a pristine shed and deck. Don't miss out on this unique property by the sea!
